name: Cash Register Samsung ER 180
description:
34180 Sam4s ER-180 Electronic Cash Register

This basic Low–Cost Commercial Grade Electronic Cash Register uses plain register paper and is designed to meet needs of many small businesses.

  • Heavy-Duty Digital Line Printer accepts 58MM (2 ¼”) receipt paper (Item # 332258)
  • Easy Paper Loading and new inker installation for even the most technically challenged
  • 16 Programmable Departments that can be preset
  • 100 Price Look-ups to automatically price up to 100 of your fastest moving items.
  • Automatic Tax Calculation added to each sale.
  • Calculator Function
  • Currency Conversion
  • 48 Position Keyboard

Specifications - 2” Wheel Type Digital Line Printer

Printer Speed: 2.2 lines per second

Paper Width: 2 ¼” (58mm) register paper (Item # 332258)

Dimensions: 12 ¾” W x 16 ½” D x 8” H

Shipping Weight: 12 lbs

Power Requirements: 120V AC

Power Consumption: Approximately 8 Watts

Memory Protection: Three AA non-Rechargeable batteries (included) will protect memory for about one year

Price: $165.95

name: Cash Register Samsung ER 180T
description:
34180T Sam4S ER-180T Electronic Cash Register

This Low-Cost Commercial Grade Thermal printer features a fast, quiet thermal printer. It is very easy to program and use. It is an incredible value for your money.

  • Fast, Quiet Thermal Printer Uses 58mm (2 ¼”) Thermal paper (Item # 01666)
  • Changing paper is a snap with the Drop and Print paper Loading
  • 16 Programmable departments
  • 500 Price Look ups means you can preprogram up to 500 fast moving items to automatically price and track sales
  • Preprogram a Receipt message on each receipt
  • Four programmable Tax Rates or Tables
  • Records sales Journal Electronically ( up to 2,500 lines)
  • Calculator Function
  • Currency Conversion
  • 48 Position Keyboard

Specifications -

  • 2” Direct Thermal Line Printer
  • Printer Speed: 7.7 Lines per second
  • Paper Width: 2 ¼” (58mm) Thermal Receipt Paper (Item# 01666)
  • Dimensions: 12 ¾: W x 16 ½” D x 8” H
  • Shipping Weight : 12 lbs
  • Power Requirements: 120V AC
  • Power Consumption : Approximately 8 Watts
  • Memory Protection: Full Charge for 24 hours will protect Memory for Approximately three years.

name: Mirror Glass Convex 13"
description:
Available in a wide variety of shapes and sizes these quality mirrors provide wide angle viewing, making it easy for you to keep an eye throughout your store. You can cut down on accidents and theft with these first line of defense mirrors. 

As a guide to ordering, many customers use a formula of 1 .inch of mirror diameter for each foot of viewing distance ..desired, noting that the larger the mirror has a more ..detailed reflected view. Therefore, a mirror with a 13" ..diameter is used for viewing a distance of up to 13 feet, a ..26" diameter for viewing up to 26 feet, and so on. Convex ..rectangular mirrors are well suited for areas with low ceiling ..heights. (If you are unsure of the size or type of mirror, ..please contact us.)

name: Steamer Reliable G-4 Standard
description:
The Reliable™ G 4 Standard Duty Steamer series of steamers are the industry leader in features, performance and value. 
    A professional steamer uses professional grade parts.
We have spent years developing our steamers with real world features that users have asked for; like our 1300 watt brass element, heavier - long life PVC steam head, wrap a round body so the bottle won’t fall off, and using industry standard parts that are interchangeable with other brands.
    Performance you can see, a name you can trust.
It’s no wonder that the G 4 series steamers have so quickly earned prominence in the industry. Once you use the G 4 steamer you’ll understand why more customers are insisting on Reliable™ brand steamers.
base_image_label: Steamer Reliable G-4 Standard base image
small_image_label: Steamer Reliable G-4 Standard small image

name: Steamer J-2 Standard Duty
description:
Jiffy® Steamer's Model J 2 Standard Duty Steamer is used in homes worldwide. Owners of our Original Model J 2 have discovered the power and versatility of steam. The Model J 2 offers the power to remove wrinkles quickly and effectively, reducing the need to iron. Steam is so gentle that you can apply it to most any fabric without fear of scorching, unlike ironing. And the Model J 2 is extremely versatile to use it to remove wrinkles on clothing, tablecloths, bedspreads, and most any fabric. This unit incorporates many of the same components found in our commercial grade steamers and, with proper maintenance, will provide years of service.
J-2 Features:
• Quick 2 minute heat up time
• 1300 watt heating element die cast in solid brass
• 50/60 Hertz electrical system
• Impact resistant 1 gallon water reservoir
• New "no spill" check valve cap
• Over 2 hours of steam per filling
• Color coded high temperature wiring
• Fusible link with automatic shut-off for safety
• 360 degree swivel casters for mobility
• Assembly wrench included
• 120 and 230 Volt units available
• Made in the USA
• Numerous cord plugs and steam head attachments available

small_image_label: Steamer J-2 Standard Duty small image

name: Steamer J-4000 Heavy Duty
description: The J-4000 Pro-Line Series is Jiffy® Steamer's most powerful model designed for commercial purposes. This J-4000 is equipped with a 5 ½ foot hose with a plastic steam head and handle and a 1 gallon self-contained water tank with preheat and steam settings. It contains a sight gauge on the side of the steamer to view water level and sediment build-up at a glance. The J-4000 heats up within 15 minutes to preheat temperature and produces steam within 2 minutes once at the preheat temperature steamer. It has a durable die cast aluminum outer housing unit with a built-in, easy-to-read water level sight gauge, 1500 watts of steaming power heating element and a stainless steel internal steam chamber.

name: Hanger Adhesive Foam Strips
description:
Keep garments hanging on hangers neatly with your choice of three different products that you can use with  hangers for your retail store
    • Hanger Covers  (100 covers/pack) 
    • Adhesive Foam Strips (1600 strips/roll). 
    • Slip-Stop Hanger Grabber
        (50 per/case, Neutral -only)
   • Hanger Retriever 54" (sold individually)
   • Hanger Stacker (sold individually)
    The Hanger Retriever (54" L-chrome plated w/wood handle) gives you the ability to reach apparel on hangers that are in hard to reach places. It is a high quality product that will last for years.  
    The Hanger Stacker - Stop wasting time untangling hangers. Designed for approx. 100 hangers. Keeps your retail store's hangers organized and easy to access for reuse.

name: Garment Rack 36"ADJ Rnd W/Rnd
description:
Adjustable Round Folding Racks and Revolving Round Racks are made of 1-1/4" round tube hang rail.  The height of the rack extends from from 48" to 66" in 3" increments. The uprights are made from 1" square tubing. 
• Rubber tipped shelf supports included.
• All Racks have swedge fitting for card holder.
• Adjustable levelers are included and casters are available.
• Add-On Rings can add a second ring to create a two-tiered round rack, Sold as sets which includes one ring and four mounting clamps. (Does not work on Revolving Rack)
    Adjustable Four Arm Topper   
• This topper fits round racks 428101, 428102, or 428109.  Four straight 10" arms.  Feature the "Theme" item on this unit and stock below.
We also carry the glass topper for all round racks. 
    This Product will be shipped via common carrier. Freight will be quoted separately. You will be notified of the freight amount.
Assembly Instructions
